{"tid":1868071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阮民安免費派發口罩要求嗌口號 恭碩良IG鬧爆引網民不滿","createTime":"2020-02-07T11:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T21:24:45.000Z","uid":50386,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"39468c82294165ab1e3d31f767388e0725ef1578","tid":1868071,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎持續蔓延，搞到人心惶惶，而香港現時口罩供應緊張，搞到唔少香港人都四出排隊撲口罩。喺一罩難求嘅環境底下，唔少良心機構及商戶都免費派發口罩俾有需要嘅人。而藝人阮民安（Tommy）噚日喺沙田石門免費派發400個口罩俾「真&bull;香港人」，吸引咗唔少人排隊。Tommy要求領取口罩嘅人講出「光復香港時代革命」等等嘅口號，先可以獲得口罩。<br />\n<br />\n呢個派口罩嘅活動有部份市民拒絕叫口號，仲反鬧工作人員。除咗有部份市民不滿即場鬧爆之外，仲引起恭碩良嘅不滿。恭碩良噚日喺IG出PO鬧爆Tommy：「I don't know this guy, but i am sure he's going to HELL...... He is not what HK people represents. I am not from HK and I am ashamed that this person even exists. Hong Kong, we can do better than this !!!! #hopelesshongkong #heartless #shameless #notalent」<span style=\"color: red;\">（我唔認識呢個人，但我可以肯定佢會落地獄。佢唔係香港人嘅代表。我唔係香港人，不過我會為呢個人嘅存在而感到羞愧。香港，我哋可以做得更好！）</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個PO出街後，引起唔少網民不滿，<span style=\"color: red;\">而恭碩良現時已經將IG帳戶刪除</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUDPXDy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUDPXDy.png&h=caf4bc9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed22c203918630e391bcf0299c18d7a64316836","tid":1868071,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"[突發]港龍工會都宣佈要搞罷工啦!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988</a>"},{"pid":"cf277bd4739cbec795dcaa78d811a89835bcd3ec","tid":1868071,"uid":238370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:42:27.000Z","msg":"加嗎嗌埋共匪死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c05e10fbb5efd92b176047e77afa712c281d420","tid":1868071,"uid":252826,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"有無發現，港豬、藍絲、廢佬、左膠大愛撚、呢一類永遠都係睇一件事係由件事中間插入黎睇.....即係佢地唔會理一開頭發生過乜事，總之呢一刻佢睇到既，就直接自己判斷果對錯，真係好on9.."},{"pid":"ce352d3f44e705c3f16145b26f019034b578f0be","tid":1868071,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:04:15.000Z","msg":"恭碩良响香港出世，澳門長大，呢刻想同香港割𥱊? 正仆街<br />\n<br />\n好彩林憶蓮醒目，睇清佢嘅為人"},{"pid":"13be7e55b765a56c769d17e5cf5e67bb279a7687","tid":1868071,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"恭碩良真係冇人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李榮浩仲多人識過咩恭碩良"},{"pid":"fbf01ee94c44fadf715f848eaaa479b92e43994e","tid":1868071,"uid":202557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce352d3f44e705c3f16145b26f019034b578f0be","tid":1868071,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:04:15.000Z","msg":"恭碩良响香港出世，澳門長大，呢刻想同香港割𥱊? 正仆街<br />\n<br />\n好彩林憶蓮醒目，睇清佢嘅為人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:34:55.000Z","msg":"Sally奶共"},{"pid":"9efba6b73d6b4e15c48f454a3ebf7ac81a8e8af7","tid":1868071,"uid":199768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbf01ee94c44fadf715f848eaaa479b92e43994e","tid":1868071,"uid":202557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce352d3f44e705c3f16145b26f019034b578f0be","tid":1868071,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:04:15.000Z","msg":"恭碩良响香港出世，澳門長大，呢刻想同香港割𥱊? 正仆街<br />\n<br />\n好彩林憶蓮醒目，睇清佢嘅為人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:34:55.000Z","msg":"Sally奶共"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:00:18.000Z","msg":"林憶蓮好係係Sandy 唔係 Sally <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff57e9ae01fee994b938614bb7d2aaa7ff891fc","tid":1868071,"uid":202557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9efb